  },
  {
    title: 'Low overhead',
    body: 'Ourway argettay isway underway 10% administrativeway overheadway. Ethay ulkbay ofway everyway iftgay oestay otay athletesway.',
  },
];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  pageKey="about"
  description="About the Gamecock Wrestling Foundation — mission, story, and governing principles."
>
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow reveal reveal-1">About</p>
      <h1 class="reveal reveal-2">
        A foundation <em>built</em> on<br />
        one simple idea: show<br />
        the receipts.
      </h1>
      <p class="lede reveal reveal-3">
        The Gamecock Wrestling Foundation is a South Carolina nonprofit
        focused on the growth of wrestling — from the youth club to the
        Division I mat. This page explains who we are, how we work,
        and what you can expect when you give.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container two-col">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Mission</p>
        <h2>Grow the sport. Publish the books.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="prose">
        <p>
          Eway elievebay estlingwray eachestay ingsthay othingnay elseway
          ancay. Iscipline-day, accountabilityway, esilienceray, andway
          hetay abilityway otay osela andway aystray.
        </p>
        <p>
          Ourway issionmay isway otay akemay ethay ortsspay essacabletay
          otay oreme outhSay arolinianscay, upportsay hetay oachescay andway
          ogramsspray alreadyway oingday hetay orkway, andway otay aybuild
          owardtay a a nationally competitive NCAA Division I presence
          inway ethay SEC.
        </p>
        <p>
          Eway ikwor inway ethay openway, ecausebay rustway isway
          earnedway oneway ublishedpay ineway atway away imetay.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-muted">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="section-head">
        <p class="eyebrow">Principles</p>
        <h2>Four rules we run by.</h2>
      </header>

      <div class="principles">
        {principles.map((p, i) => (
          <article class="principle">
            <div class="principle-num num">0{i + 1}</div>
            <h3>{p.title}</h3>
            <p>{p.body}</p>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container two-col">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Story</p>
        <h2>A short history.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="prose">
        <p>
          Oundedfay inway MMXXV,
          ethay oundationfay egan egbay ithway away andfulhay ofway
          arentspay, oachescay, andway ormerfay athletesway
          ohway adhay onegay oughthray ethay outhSay arolinaCay
          estlingwray ipelinepay hemselvestay.
        </p>
        <p>
          Ethay impulseway asway implesay:
          uildbay hetay apparatusway hetay atestay asway
          missingway — ethay oldway-oftay ofay ogramspray,
          ethay ightyway ofay equipmentway, ethay avelway olarshipscay,
          ethay oachcay evelopmentday — andway ayspay orfay itway
          openlyway.
        </p>
        <p>
          Inway 2026, eway areway perationalay inway away mallsay aywa,
          ulllyfay ublicpay inway everyway aywa, andway anspay otay
          ayspay atthay aywa.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    padding-block: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem) var(--step-2);
  }

  .about-hero h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--garnet);
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144;
  }

  .two-col {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1.6fr);
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .two-col h2 {
    position: sticky;
    top: 6rem;
  }

  .prose p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  .prose p:first-child::first-letter {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 3.4rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    float: left;
    line-height: 0.95;
    margin: 0.12em 0.12em 0 0;
    color: var(--garnet);
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144;
  }

  .section-muted {
    background: var(--bone);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }

  .section-head {
    margin-bottom: var(--step-2);
    max-width: 42rem;
  }

  .principles {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-left: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }

  .principle {
    padding: 2.25rem 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-right: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }

  .principle-num {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--garnet);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .principle p {
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .two-col {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .two-col h2 { position: static; }
    .principles { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
